<xref type="reprint from" targOrder="U" from="ROOT" to="DITTO" n="sb;6;9526" evaluate="all">SB6,9526;Cd'E30,332ff</xref></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>ἐν Ἀλεξανδρείᾳ 

    <lb n="2"/>ἀντίγραφα ἀποκριμάτων <choice><corr><supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">προ</supplied>τεθέντων</corr><sic>τεθεντων</sic></choice> ἐν τῇ στοᾷ 

    <lb n="3"/>τοῦ γυμνασίου <num value="8">η</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> Φαμενὼθ <num value="18">ιη</num>· <handShift new="m2"/> Αὐτοκράτωρ Καῖσαρ Λούκιος 


    <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Σεπ</supplied>τίμιος Σεουῆρος Εὐσεβὴς Περτίναξ Ἀραβικὸς Ἀδιαβηνικὸς Παρθικὸς μέγιστος 

    <lb n="5"/>Σεβαστὸς καὶ Αὐτοκράτωρ Καῖσαρ Μάρκος Αὐρήλιος <choice><corr>Ἀντωνῖνος</corr><sic>αντωνεινος</sic></choice> Σεβαστὸς 

    <lb n="6"/><handShift new="m1"/> Οὐλπίῳ Ἡρακλάνῳ τῷ καὶ <choice><corr>Καλλινίκῳ</corr><sic>καλλινεικω</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="7"/>τὰς ἐπιβληθείσας Ἀλεξανδρεῦσι ἢ Αἰγυπτίοις ζημί-

    <lb n="8"/>ας τῇ δωρεᾷ χρόνον προσαγα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γό</supplied>ντες ἀνήκαμεν. 

    <lb n="9"/>Ἀρτεμιδώρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῳ</supplied> τῷ καὶ <choice><corr>Ἀχιλλεῖ</corr><sic>αχιλλι</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="10"/>τοῖς ἐγνωσμένοις συνκαταθέμενος βραδέως 

    <lb n="11"/>μέμφῃ τὰ δόξαντα. 

    <lb n="12"/>Αὐρηλίοις Ἀρτεμιδώρῳ καὶ Ἀνουβίωνι καὶ ἄλλοις. 

    <lb n="13"/>τοῖς ἐγνωσμένοις <choice><corr>πείθεσθει</corr><sic>πιθεσθαι</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="14"/>Κιλ<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/>δις τῷ καὶ Μίδᾳ διὰ Φιλοκράτους υἱοῦ. 

    <lb n="15"/>ὥσπερ ἀνατραπῆναι τὴν πρᾶσιν τῶν ὑποθη-

    <lb n="16"/>κῶν οὐ δικαίως ἀξιοῖς οὕτως ἀπολαβεῖν <subst><add place="inline">σε</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">σαι</del></subst> 

    <lb n="17"/>τὴν νομὴν τῶν χωρὶς συνβάσεως κατεχομένων 

    <lb n="18"/>πρὸς βίαν χωρίων ὁ ἡγούμενος τοῦ ἔθνους <choice><corr>κελεύσει</corr><sic>κελευσι</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="19"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/>θαλγη Ἀμβ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear>ήλου διὰ Ἀβδομάνχου υἱοῦ. 

    <lb n="20"/>ἀργύριον γυναῖκες <subst><add place="inline">δανίζεσθαι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">δανιζεθαι</del></subst> καὶ ὑπὲρ ἄλλων 

    <lb n="21"/><choice><corr>ἐκτίνειν</corr><sic>εκτινιν</sic></choice> οὐ <subst><add place="inline">κωλύονται</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">κολυονται</del></subst> 

    <lb n="22"/><num value="19"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ιθ</unclear></num> ὁμοίως πρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ετέθη ἐν τῇ αὐτῇ σ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">το</unclear>ᾷ· 

    <lb n="23"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Ἀ</supplied>πόλλωνι Ἁρνεκτώτου καὶ ἄλλ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>ις. 

    <lb n="24"/>αἱ περὶ τῶν ἐπισκέψεων <choice><corr>κρίσεις</corr><sic>κρισις</sic></choice> κοινῇ <choice><corr>παρέσχον</corr><sic>παρεσχεν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="25"/>πρόνοιαν Αἰγυπτίοις. 

    <lb n="26"/>Αὐρηλίῳ Σαρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>πίωνι. 

    <lb n="27"/>τὰς ἱε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ</supplied>ω<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ύ</unclear>νας ἐκ μητρῴου γένους εἰς <choice><corr>διαδοχὴν</corr><sic>διατοχην</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="28"/>κατέρχεσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">θ</supplied>αι πρώην ἐκωλύσαμεν. 

    <lb n="29"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Π</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ</supplied>όκλῳ Ἀπολλ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ω</supplied>νίου. 

    <lb n="30"/>τοὺς γεγρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>μμένους κληρονόμους, καὶ <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> αἱ διαθῆκαι 

    <lb n="31"/>π<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>πλάσθαι λέγωνται, τῆς ν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>μῆς οὐκ ἔστιν 

    <lb n="32"/>δίκα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>ον ἐκβληθῆναι. φροντ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ί</supplied>σουσιν δὲ οἱ 

    <lb n="33"/>τὰ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> δίκας ἐπιτετραμμένοι καλέσαι τοὺς 

    <lb n="34"/>εὐ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">θ</supplied>υνομένους εἴ γε τὸ πρᾶγμά ἐστιν ἐν τῇ 

    <lb n="35"/>τάξει τῶν διαγνώσεων. 

    <lb n="36"/>Κρονίῳ Ἡρακλείδου. 

    <lb n="37"/>αἱ πρόσκαιροι νόσοι τῶν πολιτικῶν οὐκ ἀπαλλάσσου-

    <lb n="38"/><choice><corr>σιν</corr><sic>απαλλασουσιν</sic></choice> <choice><corr>λειτουργιῶν</corr><sic>λιτουργιων</sic></choice>, καὶ οἱ ἀσθενεῖς δὲ τῷ σώματι λειτουρ-

    <lb n="39"/><choice><corr><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γ</supplied>οῦσιν</corr><sic>λιτουρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γ</supplied>ουσιν</sic></choice> ἐὰν τῇ φροντίδι τῶν <choice><corr>οἰκείων</corr><sic>οικιων</sic></choice> πραγμάτων 

    <lb n="40"/><choice><corr>ἐξαρκεῖν</corr><sic>εξαρκιν</sic></choice> δύνωνται. 

    <lb n="41"/><num value="20">κ</num> ὁμοίως· 

    <lb n="42"/><choice><corr>Διοσκόρῳ</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">διοσκωρω</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">διοσκορω</del></subst></sic></choice> Ἡφαιστίωνος καὶ Πιεσῆϊ Ὀσίριος 

    <lb n="43"/>καὶ ἄλλοις. 

    <lb n="44"/>ἀργύριον ἀντὶ πυροῦ <choice><corr>καταβάλλειν</corr><sic>καταβαλλιν</sic></choice> ὑμᾶς ἐκω-

    <lb n="45"/>λύσαμεν. 

    <lb n="46"/>Ἰσιδώρῳ Δείου. 

    <lb n="47"/>τὰ μὲν ὑπὸ Κόμωνος τετολμημένα 

    <lb n="48"/><choice><corr>Φούλουϊος</corr><sic>φλουειος</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Πλαυτιανὸς</corr><sic>πλαυδιανος</sic></choice> ὁ κράτιστος ἔπαρχος 

    <lb n="49"/>τῶν στρατοπέδων καὶ οἰκεῖος ἡμῶν 

    <lb n="50"/><choice><corr>ἐξετάσει</corr><sic>εξετασι</sic></choice>. πρὸς δὲ Ἀπίωνα τὸν τελώνην, εἰ μὴ 

    <lb n="51"/><choice><corr>κοινωνεῖ</corr><sic>κοινωνι</sic></choice> τῶν ἐνκλημ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ά</supplied>των Κόμωνι, τὸν 

    <lb n="52"/>ἡγούμενον τοῦ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἔ</supplied>θνους ἕ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ξε</unclear>ις δικα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied>τήν. 

    <lb n="53"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Ἰσ</supplied>ιδώρῳ τῷ καὶ <choice><corr>Ἡρακλ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">είδ</supplied>ῃ</corr><sic><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">η</unclear>ρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>κλ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ειδ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ει</unclear></sic></choice> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">διὰ</supplied> <choice><corr><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Ἀ</supplied>πολλων<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ί</supplied>ου.</corr><sic><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>πολλωνου</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="54"/>τῆς πατρῴας κληρονομίας ἀποστὰς καὶ 

    <lb n="55"/>τὴν ἐκ τῆς ἡλικίας οὐ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κ</supplied> ἔχων βοήθειαν τῷ 

    <lb n="56"/>νόμῳ τῶν πράσεων, <choice><corr>ἐπεὶ</corr><sic>επι</sic></choice> τὴν οὐσίαν δε-

    <lb n="57"/>δημεῦσθαι φῄς, πείθ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>υ. 

    <lb n="58"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/>ελαθήῳ Καιρένου. 

    <lb n="59"/>ἐὰν τοῖς ὀρφανοῖς ἐπιτρόπους λ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ά</supplied>βῃς 

    <lb n="60"/>ἔξωθεν τάξεως, ὑπὲρ τῶν χωρίων πρὸς τοὺς 

    <lb n="61"/>νεμομένους δικαστὴς δοθήσεται. </ab></div><div n="meta.14250" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.14250" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" value="0200-03-14" notBefore="200" notAfter="200">14. März 200</date></p></div><div n="meta.14250" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.14250" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">SB</title><biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">9526</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">14250</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0094</series>; <biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">Apokrimata</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0094;6;Apokrimata" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.14250" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">88</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">60 (zu P.Col. VI 123)</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.14250" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">P.Col. VI, nach S. 6</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.14250" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Ande